title: 09/28 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (AFC); Rest of Season Rankings
description:
Before we break down the AFC home games, let's discuss some rest of season rankings and expectations for Jay Ajayi (2:20), Rob Kelley (5:10) and Chris Hogan (8:00) ... A bunch of injury news (10:50) including our thoughts on dropping Andrew Luck, TE streamers (24:00) and Week 4 bold predictions (25:30) ... We preview the AFC home games! NO-MIA (29:30), PHI-LAC (36:01), OAK-DEN (41:18), WAS-KC (46:15), CIN-CLE (51:00), CAR-NE (54:00), JAC-NYJ (59:00), PIT-BAL (1:00:40) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
